<br>
&quot;Monopolizing spawns is the intent of Vindication's going FFA. Which is clearly against Verant's policy.&quot;<br>
<br>
Auedaar nailed this one.  FFA of the sort that Vindi intends to practice here on Dro is more or less the standard on other servers.  While it'd be fun to parse the wording of the rule, or to laugh at the idea that Vindi intends to &quot;monopolize&quot; the top-end spawn, it's pointless to do so.  The fact that FFA prevails elsewhere settles the question conclusively.<br>
<br>
You can argue about the wisdom of the course Vindi has chosen.  You can, if you've got a thing for tilting at windmills, talk about issues of fairness and justice in the framework of a game largely composed of relatively anonymous heavily-armed children.  But to argue that abandoning the IGB rotation is in ANY way a violation of Verant's rules is ridiculous. <p>----------------------------------------<BR>Aanadien Jones, 60 Enchanter<BR>
